item.description:
Task View: HOXOM that Japanese Secret Society of Data Science

Maintainer:Shinya Uryu
Contact:suika1127 at gmail.com
Version:2016-03-21
We are 'HOXO-M' anonymous data analysis and R user group in Japan!!!
  • caption by dichika: NA
  • howaboutyou by dichika: NA
  • myFitbit by dichika: NA
  • myJawbone by dichika: NA
  • timecard by dichika: NA
  • yeah by dichika: sounds 'yeah'
  • retrosheet by gghatano: NA
  • densratio by hoxo-m: R Package for Density Ratio Estimation
  • fixer by hoxo-m: Tools for Fix Functions in R Packages
  • githubinstall by hoxo-m: You can install R packages on GitHub by only repository names.
  • KLIEP by hoxo-m: Kullback-Leiblar Importance Estimation Procedure (with Cross Validation)
  • magicfor by hoxo-m: magicfor - Magic Functions to Obtain Results from for Loops in R
  • mergetree by hoxo-m: NA
  • pforeach by hoxo-m: Easy to parallel processing in R
  • SparkRext by hoxo-m: SparkR extension for closer to dplyr
  • gigamonagi by teramonagi: Package of me, by me, for me in R
  • RODBCDBI by teramonagi: An implementation of R's DBI interface using ODBC package as a back-end. This allows R to connect to any DBMS that has a ODBC driver.
  • esa.io by uribo: :hatching_chick: `esa` API `v1` Wrapper Package
  • motivator by uribo: :package: Keep and improve working motivation
  • SUmisc by uribo: Personal miscellaneous :registered: Functions
  • wakatimer by uribo: :hourglass: Unofficial RStudio (IDE for R) WakaTime (https://wakatime.com) plugin.
  • rTinySegmenter by yamano357: TinySegmenter for R
  • cesiumr by yutannihilation: Cesium.js for R
  • estatapi by yutannihilation: R package for e-Stat API in Japan
  • ggPotatoL by yutannihilation: A prototype of ggHoxoM
  • highstockR by yutannihilation: An R package to draw highstock charts. This is for demonstration purpose of htmlwidgets at 46th Tokyo.R meeting.
  • kokudosuuchi by yutannihilation: 国土数値情報ダウンロードサービスWeb APIからデータを取得するためのRパッケージです
  • mukiau by yutannihilation: Face the dark.
  • qiitaddin by yutannihilation: An RStudio addin to post a knitted R Markdown file to Qiita
  • RRustFib by yutannihilation: Rust Fibonacci Calculator
  • ggfortify by sinhrks: Define fortify and autoplot functions to allow ggplot2 to handle some popular R packages.
  • DYM by kos59125: Adds 'Did you mean' feature to the R interactive
  • shadowy by kos59125: A RESTful API Framework for R
  • soracomr by kos59125: SORACOM API Client in R
